{"tid":2283973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"柴灣27歲姓廖男子墮樓亡","createTime":"2020-11-13T03:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T03:45:32.000Z","uid":122167,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"11fb612d4499e2577261c43ec791d38767c5d77b","tid":2283973,"uid":122167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:20:38.000Z","msg":"柴灣環翠邨盛翠樓，凌晨零時許，一名男子從大廈高處墮下，發出隆然巨響，倒卧在地上昏迷不醒，街坊見狀報警，救護員趕至現場，將男子送院搶救，惜終告不治，警員封鎖現場展開調查。死者27歲姓廖，相信在大廈梯間墮下，現場沒有檢獲遺書。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dqmqL29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdqmqL29.jpg&h=303fb612&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bdc2cea315ed79b825091eacbb199d4304905d36","tid":2283973,"uid":325200,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:43:19.000Z","msg":"咁少血既"},{"pid":"c6a93d192745d1ed3e4c5c1b51b074f1adf56288","tid":2283973,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994e81dd7972633c22a7cb7f2b7a02c892b4edb8","tid":2283973,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T03:45:32.000Z","msg":"足足<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}